abstract_ssm: The collection contains appraisals for properties located on Duffield Street and Willoughby Street in Downtown Brooklyn by Edmund B. Brooks, William A. Stewart, and Jacques O. Tuchler. Included with the appraisals are photographs and maps of the properties. The appraisals were conducted in relation to the urban renewal and redevelopment efforts underway in Downtown Brooklyn during this period.
